### Health check
# Returns database and cache status with metrics
# Response includes:
# - status: overall health (ok/unhealthy)
# - database: database connection status (ok/error)
# - cache: Redis cache metrics (status, hits, misses, errors, hitRate)
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/health

### Optional environment defaults for IntelliJ HTTP Client
### @name env
@host=localhost
@port=8080
